Sarpedon called. Fearing the censure of their leader,\uc0\u8232 troops made a heavy push around their counsellor king.\u8232 On the other side, the Argives reinforced their ranks\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0460\u8232 inside the wall. For both sides a major fight ensued.\u8232 Lycians, though strong, could not break the Danaan wall\u8232 and cut their way through to the ships. Danaan spearmen\u8232 could not push the Lycians back, repel them from the wall,\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[420]\u8232 now they\'92d reached it. As two men with measuring rods\u8232 quarrel over survey markers in a common field,\u8232 striving for a fair division in some narrow place,\u8232 that\'92s how the parapet kept these troops apart.\u8232 High on the wall they hacked each other\'92s armour\'97\u8232 leather bucklers and large round shields across their chests,\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0470\u8232 quivering targets. Many men were wounded,\u8232 flesh slashed with pitiless bronze, those who turned aside\u8232 and left their backs exposed while fighting and those\u8232 hit right through their shields. Everywhere along the wall,\u8232 along the parapet, men\'92s blood was spattered\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0[430]\u8232 from Trojans and Achaeans. But even so,\u8232 Trojans could not dislodge Achaeans from the wall.\u8232 Just as an industrious and honest woman\u8232 holds her scales, a weight on one side, wool on the other,\u8232 until they balance, so she can glean a pittance\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0\'a0